{"tid":1271057,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第二類勇武 懇請考慮","createTime":"2019-07-01T04:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T04:58:59.000Z","uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dddb7ba6161e32fc033fed0339e7a9145fcc5a85","tid":1271057,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZK7RPo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZK7RPo.gif&h=7aa2b0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RMD1bPr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRMD1bPr.gif&h=931cd0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">喚醒人內心嘅良知，</span><br />\n唔係一味屌或者沖擊或要協就做到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">我明白<br />\n今屆政府，唔理民意，<br />\n過去紀錄不良，用拖字訣欺騙巿民。<br />\n搬弄數據，講東講西混淆視聽。</span><br />\n<br />\n成百萬人上街都唔理，從不正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n大家想表達<br />\n想做啲野，要升級<br />\n<br />\n衝擊好好，但民心呢，有鬼點算？？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">懇請大家考慮第二類勇武。</span><br />\n<br />\n請考慮不攻擊，只推進。<br />\n老實講，人地齊裝又唔係打仗起義，<br />\n進攻打傷佢反而落口實。<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/1-gF8vW0Ddk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1-gF8vW0Ddk&h=5edcbfa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你覺得佢柒，但絕對係另一條出路。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">字眼設計</span><br />\n多用正面字，互相鼓勵，盡量減負<br />\n亦令人覺得，我地唔係咩都反對<br />\n癈佬特別討厭尼的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n可以試下：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持林鄭落台</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感恩<br />\n好人一生平安<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建伸閱讀：<br />\n放眼未來 覺醒香港行動（特長文）<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dbNncT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dbNncT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2031eaffc7242bdb670b6